chunks.html_content:
Contact HM Passport Office (HMPO) for advice or complaints about British passports issued in the UK.

There are different ways to contact HMPO depending on your circumstances.
chunks.plain_content:
Passport advice and complaints
Contact HM Passport Office (HMPO) for advice or complaints about British passports issued in the UK.
There are different ways to contact HMPO depending on your circumstances.

chunks.html_content: For questions about visas or immigration, contact UK Visas and Immigration.
chunks.plain_content:
Passport advice and complaints
For questions about visas or immigration, contact UK Visas and Immigration.

heading_context: If youre waiting for your new passport
chunks.html_content:
You can get an update by tracking your passport application. Youll need your application reference number.

You can also check how long passport applications usually take.
chunks.plain_content:
Passport advice and complaints
If youre waiting for your new passport

chunks.html_content:
For general advice, you can:

  • speak to an advisor online using web chat
  • use the online enquiry form - youll get a reply within 72 hours
  • contact HMPO by phone or post

heading_context: If you need a passport urgently
chunks.html_content: You can pay to use the Fast Track or Online Premium services to get a passport, if you think the standard service will take too long.
chunks.plain_content:
Passport advice and complaints
If you need a passport urgently
You can pay to use the Fast Track or Online Premium services to get a passport, if you think the standard service will take too long.

heading_context: If you need a passport urgently
chunks.html_content: If youve already applied for a passport and have not received it, do not apply again using the Fast Track or Online Premium services. You will not get your passport sooner or get a refund.
chunks.plain_content:
Passport advice and complaints
If you need a passport urgently
If youve already applied for a passport and have not received it, do not apply again using the Fast Track or Online Premium services. You will not get your passport sooner or get a refund.

heading_context: If you need a passport urgently
chunks.html_content:
Call the Passport Adviceline if you need to travel urgently because:

  • you need medical treatment
  • a friend or family member is seriously ill or has died
  • youre working for, or are representing, the government
